lead_paragraph: Purdue sophomore forward Caleb Swanigan joined some elite company Friday night during the 15th-ranked Boilermakers' 109-65 season-opening victory over McNeese State.

headline.print_headline: No. 15 Boilers Ride Swanigan to Blowout Victory
